-- Afren Says Seven Foreigners, Including One Canadian, Kidnapped in Nigeria
-- B y   E d u a r d   G i s m a t u l l i n
-- 2010-11-09T09:28:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-09/afren-says-seven-foreigners-including-one-canadian-kidnapped-in-nigeria.html
Afren Plc said a total of seven
foreign workers were kidnapped in Nigeria. Two French nationals,
two Indonesians, two U.S. citizens and one Canadian were taken,
a company spokesman said by telephone today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eduard Gismatullin in London at 
